class:: TDelay
summary:: Trigger delay.
categories::  UGens>Triggers, UGens>Delays


Description::

Delays a trigger by a given time. Any triggers which arrive in the time
between an input trigger and its delayed output, are ignored.


classmethods::

method::ar, kr

argument::in

Input trigger signal.


argument::dur

Delay time in seconds.


Examples::

code::

({
	z = [Impulse, Blip].choose.ar(2);
	[z * 0.1, [ToggleFF, Trig].choose.ar(TDelay.ar(z, 0.5)) * [SinOsc, FSinOsc, SinOscFB].choose.ar(mul: 0.1)]
}.scope)

